Dietary supplements also play a crucial role in the nutritional food market, catering to individuals who may have dietary restrictions or require additional nutrients to meet their daily requirements. These products, which include vitamins, minerals, amino acids, enzymes, and herbal supplements, offer a convenient solution for filling nutritional gaps in one's diet. The dietary supplements segment is expected to witness steady growth as consumers increasingly embrace a holistic approach to health and wellness.

